  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nWhen the debugger is attached to a target and that target crashes, any pending commands will be re-run once the target has been loaded again.  \n  \nUsing this behavior, an extension with a devtools_page entry can crash a target page via an (indirect) Runtime.evaluate call"
